        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>Position Summary: </strong> The Shingo Institute is part of the Jon M. Huntsman School of Business at USU. We’re looking for someone with experience in graphic art, branding, and print. In this position, you will be the brand boss; the one who sees to it that everything that goes out is branded properly. You’ll be part of a small marketing and communications team that includes student employees and you’ll report to the Marketing and Communications Manager. You’ll design logos, booklets, signage, web pages, brochures, and you’ll edit the work of others in order to brand it properly and make certain that it looks impressive and professional. You’ll have a big hand in shaping the public image of the Shingo Institute. You may also be asked to do other marketing related tasks beyond graphic art. Here, we help each other wherever we’re needed. Learn more about the Shingo Institute at Shingo.org. 
 
        </p>
