                <li>Print experience (preflights, press checks, etc.).</li>
                <li>Experience with branding beyond just logo placement.</li>
                <li>Proficiency with Adobe Dreamweaver.</li>
                <li>Ability to accept changes to your work without having your ego bruised (everyone gets edited here, no exceptions).</li>
